snippet.title: Strinova Season 1 Gameplay Trailer#strinova
snippet.description:
Get the first drop in our official launch of the game and take on actions with New Agents, Maps, Legendary Skins and more. Eika's Explosive Fireballs may illuminates the opponents, while Fragrans's Euphoric Aroma can heal the team. What's more? PLAY NOW and discover more!

Welcome to STRINOVA! A free-to-play 5v5 Anime-Style Shooter game. The game is available on PC hhttps://strinova.link/keK6o and Steam https://strinova.link/1p3gvV
